## Auto-Scaling Policy

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| CPU Threshold | 70% |
| Check Interval | Every 5 seconds |
| Cooldown Period | 5 minutes |
| Max Instances | 3 |
| Machine Type | e2-micro (GCP free tier) |
| Zone | asia-south2-a |
| Scale-out trigger | CPU > 70% for one check cycle |

